strings.Value: "Do you know where your shaman Tartuk is?"
"Friendsss! Chief wait! Many trapsss. Follow me!"
"Don't know! Asssk Chief! Chief know all!"

"Mine!" {n}The kobold is obviously proud of his knowledge.{/n} "Humansss make, then leave. Kobold come, live, work. Was mite passsage, no more. Mite thief! Mite ambushhh attack, we break passsage, lose big chessst, goodsss. Can't go deep. Ssscary. Angry mite bug, wild bug live down there."
